      SUBROUTINE C4DTA (C4L,V)                                          c4dt 100
C **  N2 CONTINUUM                                                      c4dt 110
      COMMON /C4C8/ C4(133),C8(102)                                     c4dt 120
      C4L=0.                                                            c4dt 130
